'''日本仿厚蟹'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Helicana japonica''}}）为[[方蟹科|方蟹科]][[仿厚蟹属|仿厚蟹属]]的动物。分布于[[朝鲜|南韓]][[德积岛|德積島]]、[[日本|日本]]南部以及[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]的[[山东|山东]]等地，生活环境为海水，多见于穴居于泥滩或泥岸上。<ref name='id12031'/><ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|title=Taxonomy, phylogeny, and biogeography of the endemic mudflat crab Helicel Chasmagnathus complex (Crustacea: Brachyura: Varunidae) from East Asia|author=Shih, Hsi-Te, and Hiroshi Suzuki.|url=https://decapoda.nhm.org/pdfs/31797/31797.pdf|journal=Zoological Studies|issue=1|year=2008|volume=47|page=114-125|access-date=2021-06-10|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414163941/https://decapoda.nhm.org/pdfs/31797/31797.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite journal|title=Revision of the Helice/Chasmagnathus complex (Crustacea: Decapoda: Brachyura)|url=http://www.vliz.be/en/datasets-belgian-coast-and-sea?module=ref&refid=250473|last=Sakai|first=K.|last2=Türkay|first2=M.|date=2006|journal=Abhandlungen der Senckenbergischen Naturforschenden Gesellschaft|language=en|last3=Yang|first3=S.-L.|access-date=2021-06-10|archive-date=2021-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210610143215/http://www.vliz.be/en/datasets-belgian-coast-and-sea?module=ref&refid=250473|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 物種分類 ==
日本仿厚蟹原名日本厚蟹，於1980年仿厚蟹屬從厚蟹屬分離出來後，被歸類於仿厚蟹屬下的一種，因此改為日本仿厚蟹。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Notes on some Japanese and Chinese Helice with Helice (Helicana) n. subgen., including Helice (Helicana) japonica n. sp.(Crustacea: Decapoda)|date=1980|journal=Senckenberg. Biol|volume=60|page=393-411|author1=Katsushi Sakai|coauthors=Yatsuzuka}}</ref>

